{"tid":1198912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"未來抗爭總方向：和理非嘅真正意義","createTime":"2019-06-10T10:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T12:07:22.000Z","uid":160637,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0c6debe5a37f3d9911c203e998f55cc6c0aff9f","tid":1198912,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:57:51.000Z","msg":"呢度講嘅和理非唔係話唔可以衝，而係和理非噉衝。<br />\n<br />\n<del>和平</del>&mdash;&mdash;我覺得即係非暴力，無需強調。<br />\n理性&mdash;&mdash;有策略噉抗爭，避免情緒化。硬碰硬唔掂咪食腦，保持清醒。<br />\n非暴力&mdash;&mdash;爭取最大支持。始終社會主流睇嘢較印象式、較片面，好多人以表面判斷對錯。非暴力亦避免我哋自己成為惡。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭唔應該成為情緖發洩，唔好做多餘嘅嘢。我哋要贏嘅唔止係一埸戰役，更加係一場長遠嘅戰爭。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b0abdc5633501b38336ad1767e08cc8584fd21e2","tid":1198912,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbaf46cd58bee0ae51785d3cf2c21d3dd7bb587a","tid":1198912,"uid":116087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"點樣非暴力咁衝呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594817a3174e87832c6bf544871af21016afb66f","tid":1198912,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fbaf46cd58bee0ae51785d3cf2c21d3dd7bb587a","tid":1198912,"uid":116087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"點樣非暴力咁衝呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"衝撞警方防線同暴力針對警員唔同"},{"pid":"a6345588b89de662d1fb0cf28cf7e0c1381b3b85","tid":1198912,"uid":160637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dadcdb75de5e02b373e7d1ec5c3c50d5f2eea9e","tid":1198912,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T